 in-state rentals, out-of-state rentals, residential development, stocks - E-Book avail.", "entities": {"description": {}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "linktr.ee/thinkappraiser", "expanded_url": "https://linktr.ee/thinkappraiser", "indices": [0, 23], "url": "https://t.co/8WbUnYM4EH"}]}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {}, "card": null, "place": {}, "entities": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "timestamps": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": [{"id_str": "479682437", "indices": [0, 13], "name": "Holly Lin \u2b55\ufe0f", "screen_name": "thehollylin1"}]}, "quoted_tweet": null, "retweeted_tweet": null, "isLimitedReply": false, "communityInfo": null, "article": null}, {"type": "tweet", "id": "2051172561291977065", "url": "https://x.com/Fibonacci69/status/2051172561291977065", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/Fibonacci69/status/2051172561291977065", "text": "What if you could predict a home\u2019s sale price almost perfectly\u2026 without ever stepping inside?\n\nSeby Rubino reveals the dashboard of @resilabsai, a real estate super intelligence \n\nEvery single day, ResiLabs runs a global competition.\n\nAI engineers build pricing models, upload them to Hugging Face, and submit them.\n\nThen ResiLabs tests each model:\n\nHow accurately can it predict what a house will actually sell for?\n\nAt the end of the day, the best-performing model gets selected, tested internally, and integrated into the product.\n\nThat means the system improves\u2026 every single day\n\nRight now, the top model is hitting 98.67% accuracy\n\nSo when ResiLabs predicts a home\u2019s price, it\u2019s usually within about 1\u20132% of the actual sale price\n\nSometimes it misses slightly.\n\nSometimes it\u2019s almost exact, down to a fraction of a percent.\n\nAnd here\u2019s the crazy part \n\nResiLabs built this entire system for about $245,000\n\nFor comparison, @zillow spent roughly $25 million on its pricing system, Zestimate \n\nThis product doesn\u2019t just scale\n\nIt evolves, every day", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 3, "replyCount": 4, "likeCount": 11, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 93, "createdAt": "Mon May 04 05:30:22 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 0, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2051172561291977065", "displayTextRange": [0, 276], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "Fibonacci69", "url": "https://x.com/Fibonacci69", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/Fibonacci69", "id": "1475750433381617664", "name": "Fibonacci \ud83e\udd77", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1945902236820754432/bO8ZAeD9_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1475750433381617664/1752774220", "description": "", "location": "No Man's Land", "followers": 3813, "following": 3468, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": false, "createdAt": "Tue Dec 28 08:48:27 +0000 2021", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 79589, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 2325, "statusesCount": 29937, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2050530741985890363"], "profile_bio": {"description": "iTrade | iClip \u2702\ufe0f", "entities": {"description": {}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {"media": [{"additional_media_info": {"monetizable": false}, "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/A7r79lN6bS", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/Fibonacci69/status/2051172561291977065/video/1", "ext_media_availability": {"status": "Available"}, "id_str": "2051172275177598976", "indices": [277, 300], "media_key": "7_2051172275177598976", "media_results": {"id": "QXBpTWVkaWFSZXN1bHRzOgwAAwoAARx3OlETFzAACgACHHc6k7DWIWkAAA==", "result": {"__typename": "ApiMedia", "id": "QXBp